'''瞬态电压感受器阳离子通道，子类A，成员1'''（简称'''TRPA1'''）是一种由人类[[基因|基因]]''TRPA1''所编码的一种蛋白（其它生物由Trpa1基因所编码）<ref name="pmid10066796">{{cite journal en| author = Jaquemar D, Schenker T, Trueb B | title = An ankyrin-like protein with transmembrane domains is specifically lost after oncogenic transformation of human fibroblasts | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 274 | issue = 11 | pages = 7325–33 | pmid = 10066796 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.274.11.7325 | url =  | issn = |date=March 1999}}</ref><ref name="pmid16382100">{{cite journal en| author = Clapham DE, Julius D, Montell C, Schultz G | title = International Union of Pharmacology. XLIX. Nomenclature and structure-function relationships of transient receptor potential channels | journal = Pharmacol. Rev. | volume = 57 | issue = 4 | pages = 427–50 | pmid = 16382100 | doi = 10.1124/pr.57.4.6 | url = | issn = |date=December 2005}}</ref>。

==功能==
TRPA1含有14个重复的N-端[[锚蛋白|锚]]，属于[[瞬态电压感受器通道|瞬态电压感受器通道]]中的一种，它被认为起到机械压力感觉器官的作用<ref name="pmid17217068">{{cite journal en| author = García-Añoveros J, Nagata K | title = TRPA1 | journal = Handb Exp Pharmacol | volume = | issue = 179 | pages = 347–62 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17217068 | doi = 10.1007/978-3-540-34891-7_21 | url = | issn = }}</ref>。尽管目前对于该蛋白的具体功能尚不明确，然而有研究指出该蛋白涉及了[[信号转换|信号转换]]的一个步骤，以及涉及了对[[细胞生长|细胞生长]]的控制<ref>{{cite web | title = Entrez Gene: TRPA1 transient receptor potential cation channel, subfamily A, member 1| url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=gene&Cmd=ShowDetailView&TermToSearch=8989| accessdate = }}</ref>。

最近的研究指出，TRPA1可以被多种活性化合物所激活，如[[丙烯基异硫氰酸酯|丙烯基异硫氰酸酯]]、[[肉桂醛|肉桂醛]]、法尼基硫代[[水杨酸|水杨酸]]、[[尼古丁|尼古丁]]及其结构类似物<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www-brs.ub.ruhr-uni-bochum.de/netahtml/HSS/Diss/SherkheliMAzhar/Zusammenfassung.pdf|title=合成|access-date=2009-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018013221/http://www-brs.ub.ruhr-uni-bochum.de/netahtml/HSS/Diss/SherkheliMAzhar/Zusammenfassung.pdf|archive-date=2017-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[福尔马林|福尔马林]]、[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]、[[4-羟基壬烯醛|4-羟基壬烯醛]]以及[[丙烯醛|丙烯醛]]。这一蛋白被认为是人体的一个[[化学感受器|化学感受器]]<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Tai C, Zhu S, Zhou N |title=TRPA1: the central molecule for chemical sensing in pain pathway? |journal=J. Neurosci. |volume=28 |issue=5 |pages=1019–21 |pmid=18234879 |doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.5237-07.2008|date=January 2008}}</ref>。通过研究发现，去除了Trpa1基因的实验鼠，对于能造成痛觉得福尔马林完全没有感觉<ref>{{cite journal en|author=McNamara CR, Mandel-Brehm J, Bautista DM, ''et al.'' |title=TRPA1 mediates formalin-induced pain |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. |volume=104 |issue=33 |pages=13525–30 |pmid=17686976 |pmc=1941642 |doi=10.1073/pnas.0705924104|date=August 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|author=McMahon SB, Wood JN |title=Increasingly irritable and close to tears: TRPA1 in inflammatory pain |journal=Cell |volume=124 |issue=6 |pages=1123–5 |pmid=16564004 |doi=10.1016/j.cell.2006.03.006|date=March 2006}}</ref>。针对TRPA1的拮抗剂，对于缓解包括所有[[弗氏佐劑|弗氏佐劑]]及福尔马林造成的炎症所引起的疼痛都是有效的。

虽然目前仍无法确切证明机体内的TRPA1对于有害的冷冻感觉起到了传导作用，然而近期的研究已明确表明至少在试管内TRPA1通道会因为冷冻而激活<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Sawada Y, Hosokawa H, Hori A, Matsumura K, Kobayashi S |title=Cold sensitivity of recombinant TRPA1 channels |journal=Brain Res. |volume=1160 |issue= |pages=39–46 |pmid=17588549 |doi=10.1016/j.brainres.2007.05.047|date=July 2007}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|author=Klionsky L, Tamir R, Gao B, ''et al.'' |title=Species-specific pharmacology of Trichloro(sulfanyl)ethyl benzamides as transient receptor potential ankyrin 1 (TRPA1) antagonists |journal=Mol Pain |volume=3 |issue= |pages=39 |year=2007 |pmid=18086308 |pmc=2222611 |doi=10.1186/1744-8069-3-39}}</ref>。

==临床意义==
科学家们于2008年发现，[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]会抑制人类TRPA1通道的活性，然而实验鼠感觉神经上的TRPA1通道却会引起对含[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]饮料的抗拒，这暗示着该通道能传导对咖啡因的知觉<ref name="pmid18988737">{{cite journal en| author = Nagatomo K, Kubo Y | title = Caffeine activates mouse TRPA1 channels but suppresses human TRPA1 channels | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = | issue = | pages = | pmid = 18988737 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.0809769105 | url = | issn = |date=November 2008}}</ref>。除此之外，某些烟民在使用尼古丁替代疗法来戒烟时，会出现皮肤刺激感甚至过敏，也和TRPA1通道不无关系。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Talavera K, Gees M, Karashima Y, ''et al.'' | title = Nicotine activates the chemosensory cation channel TRPA1 | journal = Nature Neuroscience | volume = | issue = | pages = | doi = 10.1038/nn.2379 | url = | issn = |date=September 2009}}</ref>

